    "body": "> #### Expected Behavior\n> `PIPESTATUS` gets updated showing values for all return values for the last pipeline.\n\n`PIPESTATUS` is an array, so you should use `echo \"${PIPESTATUS[@]}\"` to get all values. You used `$PIPESTATUS` to check the values, but `$PIPESTATUS` is equivalent to the first element `${PIPESTATUS[0]}`.\n",
